KPI Dashboard
Overview

The KPI Dashboard monitors the performance of the Happy Insurance Voice Agent. It helps evaluate customer experience, automation efficiency, authentication success, and backend API performance.

Key Performance Indicators
Total Conversations – Number of customer conversations handled by the AI.
Authentication Success Rate – Percentage of users successfully authenticated.
Automation Rate – Percentage of queries resolved without human intervention.
Escalation Rate – Percentage of conversations transferred to a human agent.
Average Handling Time (AHT) – Average time taken to resolve a customer request.
API Success Rate – Percentage of successful backend API/tool calls.
Dashboard Insights
Most customer queries were resolved successfully by the AI.
Authentication was completed successfully for the majority of users.
Policy inquiries and claim status were the most frequently requested services.
Low escalation rate indicates effective AI-assisted customer support.
Backend APIs responded successfully with low latency, ensuring a smooth user experience.
